Start
/ Failure — param resolution failure (bad scheme / unset %var% / convert) returns a typed Data error,
/ NOT an NRE. The await→guard→use pattern catches it at the post-await guard.
- read file 's3://bucket/key'
    on error call SchemeError
    write to %never%
- assert %schemeKey% equals "SchemeNotRegistered"

SchemeError
- set %schemeKey% = %!error.Key%
